{"tid":1001881,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友對隻狗仲好過我","createTime":"2019-01-30T13:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T15:39:30.000Z","uid":431,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d69922dc70901c6ce69d8513612d3aec5d22ee77","tid":1001881,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"我男朋友係終極狗痴來 成日都帶隻狗去做高級寵物美容<br />\n又會畀啲靚牛肉同新鮮雞肉佢食<br />\n仲有經常買啲卡通衫佢著 放狗嗰陣又會畀佢著鞋<br />\n聽佢講一個月洗費都要4k起跳 好鬼誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反 我生日/拍拖紀念日同啲大時大節都唔會話送禮物過我<br />\n咁本身我哋出街所有洗費都已經係aa 上次拍拖紀念日我想話食好少少去放題<br />\n佢竟然話貴想食平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰下我真係有少少嬲即刻黑咗面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來已經餐餐m記譚仔無所謂 難得大日子想話食好少少都唔得 又唔係要佢請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係諗唔明點解佢咁肯dump錢落隻狗度但又唔肯同我食好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4a6fc451e7373e800d6c805e1a915c00d001f2","tid":1001881,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"我隻狗=你"},{"pid":"f232218495c3e6dbfe27af18a9a90f8cd29a6de0","tid":1001881,"uid":30708,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:24:09.000Z","msg":"咁係因為佢聰明啫"},{"pid":"899c302c7984a5e2620965dbe1ed8f57af5e8558","tid":1001881,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:25:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5319d0a550906f5d3e87543abd8b9996b932f9c9","tid":1001881,"uid":2234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"狗都不如囉"},{"pid":"5bfa2aaac7fcb07bb64f67d16c0a6d1866dff0fb","tid":1001881,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd4a6fc451e7373e800d6c805e1a915c00d001f2","tid":1001881,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"我隻狗=你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01