e":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"你試著卡通衫扮狗，之前同佢狗仔式，一定可以得佢歡心。"},{"pid":"9f3095545c492f38042ee619a0256ef3e2730e63","tid":1001881,"uid":196459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:36:00.000Z","msg":"我都係愛隻狗多過我男友<br />\n因為隻狗呢一世永遠得我一個<br />\n而男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28b9c26948b1c42d30820e778238b829f378a1b","tid":1001881,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"走啦 <br />\n痴線佬嚟<br />\n<br />\n隻狗死嗰陣分分鐘陪埋佢落去"},{"pid":"a51ea99f759c2ddeae981c3e56ccd3b418bc3a27","tid":1001881,"uid":220853,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"對隻狗仔黎講 主人就係佢既全部<br />\n而你個男朋友只係你既一部份 你仲擁有好多<br />\n所以任何人對寵物 比人類更好 係非常合理既事<br />\n如果你覺得你男朋友對隻狗仲好過對你 係反智行為的話<br />\n你既思想好有問題"},{"pid":"3b4b31f85130bbc66bf6d8d940f906d224c4dd98","tid":1001881,"uid":158976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"你男朋友而家真係雞犬不寧..."},{"pid":"a5c42fb21a974c0fe78c71d54f47fd7058604eee","tid":1001881,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:47:35.000Z","msg":"依啲賤人要屌返佢屎眼教訓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6303d77c80454fe0d23e7e690ee68ae995472df9","tid":1001881,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:54:23.000Z","msg":"你識唔識狗仔式先"},{"pid":"a40f455ca4e328a4f6be909962b96ecbd6530a5c","tid":1001881,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"汪"},{"pid":"5665d53277ef5118102402e9e312ece5ebc36c7e","tid":1001881,"uid":15473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"支持"}]}